:"<p>When you buy Handmade, you support the dream of a person who puts their heart and soul into making chikankari special.<\/p>","button_url":"shopify:\/\/pages\/our-story","button_text":""}}},"block_order":["item_74hTfX"],"settings":{"full_width":true,"images_layout":"stacked","collage_images_alignment":"middle","background":"#f7f7f7","background_gradient":"","text_color":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":""}},"testimonials_ixf9yp":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonial_UaVxJR":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_4271.heic","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"M.G","title":"","content":"<p>Received my combo of Lavender and Black kurta first but I wanted to exchange black one due to size issues and Adhya just accepted my request, in addition they also obliged by sending green color which I liked in exchange of black. It was sweet of them to send a hand written note and a pair of earrings as a gift. How cute is that..Thank you Adhya. I'll definitely make you my go to chikankari place<\/p>"}},"testimonial_eC3NMT":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/WhatsApp_Image_2024-09-24_at_12.26.21_PM.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"kirti pandey","title":"Most comfiest Kurtis 💛","content":"<p>It's my third wash still color didn't fade and fabric didn't shrink. Very comfortable fabric for using regularly. I ordered more 2 colors💛 As a makeup artist I have to travel and go on stages. This Kurti is perfect because it's breadthable and most imp very comfortable😍🤞Thankyou adhya chikankari for this wonderful kurtis<\/p>"}},"testimonial_EFez83":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/WhatsApp_Image_2024-09-26_at_6.14.00_PM.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"Siddhi Naik","title":"Beautifully Crafted Adhya Chikankari Kurti -A Must-Have!","content":"<p>recently bought a Chikankari kurti from Adhya, and I'm absolutely thrilled with it! So happy with my purchase! The kurti is stunning and the fabric feels amazing. I highly recommend this elegant and comfortable kurti from Adhya! Thank you, Adhya!💗<\/p>"}},"testimonial_WPP38X":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/0a5b9bf7-d34c-41f3-a51f-edccd8b5c98c.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"Soumita Ghosh","title":"love this kurtis","content":"<p>i have received my order<br\/>yesterday.Lovely colour and design and very soft material. Thank you💗<\/p>"}},"testimonial_AHtaBL":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/WhatsApp_Image_2024-09-26_at_6.14.46_PM.jpg","round_avatar":true,"show_rating":true,"rating":5,"author":"Arpita","title":"","content":"<p>By the way, the Kurtis are too good and earrings as well.. fit colour Everything is perfect 😍.it is actully value for money.fabric vey soft and perfect for everyday wear.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["testimonial_UaVxJR","testimonial_eC3NMT","testimonial_EFez83","testimonial_WPP38X","testimonial_AHtaBL"],"settings":{"full_width":true,"stack_testimonials":false,"subheading":"","title":"Customers reviews","content":"<p>Read what our customers say.<\/p>","link_url":"","link_text":"","background":"","background_gradient":"","text_color":"","heading_color":"","heading_gradient":"","testimonial_card_background":"","testimonial_card_text_color":""}},"before-after-image":{"type":"before-after-image","settings":{"full_width":true,"subheading":"","title":"Adorn Yourself with Timeless Craftsmanship","content":"<p>At Adhya Chikankari, we are dedicated to preserving the essence of authentic Chikankari craftsmanship. Each kurti is meticulously hand-embroidered by skilled artisans who have mastered this traditional art form. Every stitch tells a story of heritage, with intricate designs that take time, precision, and dedication to complete. Our focus is on creating ethnic wear that honor this age-old craft while ensuring timeless elegance and comfort. When you choose Adhya Chikankari, you’re not just wearing a kurti—you’re embracing the legacy of original Chikankari, brought to life by the hands of true artisans.<\/p>","before_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/chapai.png","before_image_mobile":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/chapai.png","after_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_7012.jpg","after_image_mobile":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_7012.jpg","expand_image":true,"text_position":"start","before_after_text_position":"top","before_text":"","after_text":"","drag_initial_position":50,"background":"#f7f7f7","background_gradient":"","text_color":"","before_text_color":"#ffffff","after_text_color":"#ffffff","drag_cursor_background":"#ffffff","drag_cursor_color":"#000000"}},"newsletter_Kawdrt":{"type":"newsletter","disabled":true,"settings":{"full_width":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/now_8.png","show_icon":true,"title":"Newsletter","content":"<p><strong>Sign up now and receive a FREE pair of oxidized earrings with your first purchase!<\/strong> Plus, be the first to know about exclusive offers and latest arrivals.<\/p>","button_text":"Subscribe","subtext":"","background":"#f7f7f7","background_gradient":"","text_color":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":""}}},"order":["slideshow","scrolling_text_GtdaQe","featured-collection","17273466324463fe67","featured_collection_MWKDhW","multiple_images_with_text_MydGjE","media_grid_FMthgY","1727347439f3f8fea8","scrolling_text_6FAqWL","multiple_images_with_text_VhMhkX","testimonials_ixf9yp","before-after-image","newsletter_Kawdrt"]}